d surprisingly controversial — images of the coronavirus pandemic that’s been tearing through the US for more than two months now. My local Target store, for example, now keeps customers lined up outside the front door, welcoming in people gradually to keep that number limited inside.<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">&nbsp;The states where this is illegal are as follows:</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 23px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: disc; line-height: 26px;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Connecticut</strong></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Hawaii</strong></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Delaware</strong></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">New York</strong></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Massachusetts</strong></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Illinois</strong></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Rhode Island</strong></li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">New York was one of the first states that required people to wear a mask in public when social distancing is impractical.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><a href="https://bgr.com/2020/05/21/face-mask-required-by-law-in-states-stop-spread-of-coronavirus/" style="background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 800; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important;">Read More</a></p></div></div></div></div></div>',
