                'title' => 'All you need to know about death penalty',
                'posted_by' => 'Cochran Firm California',
                'image' => 'storage/news/news30.webp',
                'select_option' => "OP ED'S",
                'sub_title' => 'COCHRAN LA',
                'short_description' => 'There were 55 women on death row in the United States as of July 1, 2018, the most recent date for which data is available from the Criminal Justice Project.',
                'description' => '<div class="el__leafmedia el__leafmedia--sourced-paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;  color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><p class="zn-body__paragraph speakable" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Here’s a look at the death penalty in the United States.</p></div><div class="zn-body__paragraph speakable" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;  color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Facts:&nbsp;</u></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">As of October 11, 2018, capital punishment is<a href="http://www.deathpenaltyinfo.org/documents/FactSheet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">&nbsp;legal in 30 US states.</a></div><div class="zn-body__read-all" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;  color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">&nbsp;<br></div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Federal Government:</u></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">The US government and US military have&nbsp;<a href="https://deathpenaltyinfo.org/federal-death-row-prisoners" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">63 people awaiting execution</a>&nbsp;as of December 21, 2018.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">The US government has&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bop.gov/about/history/federal_executions.jsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">executed three people</a>&nbsp;since 1988 when the federal death penalty statute was reinstated.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Females:</u></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">There were<a href="https://deathpenaltyinfo.org/women-and-death-penalty#facts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">&nbsp;55 women on death row</a>&nbsp;in the United States as of July 1, 2018, the most recent date for which data is available from the Criminal Justice Project.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Sixteen women have been executed since the reinstatement of the death penalty (as of December 31, 2017).</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Juveniles:</u></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">Twenty-two individuals were executed between 1976 and 2005 for&nbsp;<a href="http://www.deathpenaltyinfo.org/execution-juveniles-us-and-other-countries#execsus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">crimes committed as juveniles.</a></div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">March 1, 2005 –&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://www.law.cornell.edu/supct/html/03-633.ZS.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">Roper v. Simmons.</a>&nbsp;The Supreme Court rules that the execution of juvenile offenders is unconstitutional.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Clemency:</u></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">Since 1976,&nbsp;<a href="https://deathpenaltyinfo.org/clemency" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">288 individuals have been granted clemency</a>.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">For federal death row inmates, the president alone has the power to grant a pardon.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Timeline:</u></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">1834 –&nbsp;</strong>Pennsylvania becomes the first state to move executions into correctional facilities, ending public executions.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">1846 –</strong>Michigan becomes the first state to abolish the death penalty for all crimes except treason.</div><div class="zn-body__paragraph" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">1890 –</strong>William Kemmler becomes the first person executed by electrocution.</div></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;  color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">&nbsp;<br></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline;  color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><a href="https://deathpenaltyinfo.org/documents/FactSheet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(229, 196, 101) !important; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">Read More</a></div>',
